## Limitations

This report is based on data and analyses available up to October 2023. The findings are subject to the limitations of the data sources, including potential biases in the analyses conducted by various organizations. Additionally, the long-term effects of the TCJA on the middle class may not be fully captured in the data from the initial years following its implementation. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more comprehensive evaluation.

